    <p>{`Next we decided to stay with our upperclass theme and make an obligatory stop by one of the most famous stores in the world: Harrods. This store which is housed in a building that looks like may have been a palace in its past, is just as decorative on the inside. Of course it is full of expensive flashy labels, but it also sells ordinary food. I ask you does your grocery store have a chandelier in it? Because this place does!`}</p>
